data.description: UNIQUE Horse property with a beautiful home, 5* stables and arena on 6.8 acres. Stunning driveway between the ponds and up to the house. Cathedral ceilings in the living room with gorgeous views from the picture window over the pond. Large Dining Room and Granite counter tops in the upscale country kitchen with a large pantry. The spacious master bedroom suite on main floor has a gorgeous, attached sunroom lounge, deluxe bathroom and WIC. Upstairs the SECOND MASTER has amazing views over the pond and a third bedroom and office/study room. 5 STAR stables behind with paddocks and dressage arena and sheds. USDF large dressage arena with rubber/composite footing, handsome 4-stall barn; Tack & Feed Rooms; wash stall; turnout paddocks; 3-board fencing. Massive wired workshop with shed for covered parking and equipment. A full media room in the basement and attached 2 car garage Charming indoor living spaces bring the outdoors inside. Whole house Generator! Septic permit is for 3 Bedrooms, but there are numerous multi-functional rooms. New Roof and Skylights over 100k+ of new upgrades!
